ay.\r\n\r\ni\'m not driven by hype, how limited a shoe is and have no loyalty to any particular brand or style but if i had to call my top five sneaker silhouettes it\'d be the vans half cab and the chukka, nike air huarache light, asics gel-lyte III and the gt-II\r\n\r\nworking in the industry definitely helps feed my habit but there\'s nothing more satisfying that hunting down a hard to find release and having it arrive on your doorstep a few days later.\r\n\r\ni cant see myself ever losing interest in collecting sneakers but as i\'ve got older my tastes have definitely changed, my purchases are more thought out now and what turns me to a shoe has certainly changed from five years ago.\r\n\r\nits pleasing to know that ive got a ten year old son who\'s heir to my collection and he\'s there to take over the mantle as and when its time for me to hang up my shoes. a kind of mini-me if you like... which means im safe in the knowledge my collection will go to a good home as he loves his kicks as much as i do... if not more!!','sneakers',0,0,'4 times a month','my kids and my work... and i like a drink.',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:0;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:1;s:5:\"buddy\";b:1;s:7:\"message\";b:1;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2008-05-21 12:09:40'),(582,586,'casual','1971-02-09','f','91355','United States','US','www.LynndaRakos.com','right now I just put up one of the original prints used on the set of MTVs Real World on Ebay! Check it out at:\r\n\r\nhttp://cgi.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?ViewItem&item=120264821875\r\n','antique robots, jetsons','robots',0,0,'','',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:0;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:1;s:5:\"buddy\";b:1;s:7:\"message\";b:1;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2008-05-22 13:42:38'),(583,587,'casual','1944-10-27','m','94704','United States','US','','',' I mostly seek early model \'Reach\' toothbrushes or foreign toothbrushes with all white bristles. For DVDs