ot only do snowglobes come in a variety of sizes and shapes, they are also sturdy and portable. Each finely crafted scenic detail in a globe adds a nice complimentary touch to one\'s travel memoirs.\r\n\r\nThe majority of my collection are ball-like glass globe with a 45mm diameter, however, any globe below 55mm diameter are also counted as mini globes and I have some of those in my collection. \r\nI collect all categories including Advertising, Angels, Animals, Characters, Designers, Holidays and Celebrations, Location, Movies, Religious, Sports, and Dual-purpose globes. \r\n\r\nI also collect snow globe related items like snow globe in print and TV, books, fabrics, clothes, cards, posters, mugs, wine cock, mattress, ties, pins and others.\r\n','Snowglobe',4200,30000,'3 times a month','My hobby in collecting snowglobes all started In Christmas 2000, when my then boyfriend (now my husband Raymond Chung) gave me a beautiful golf ball size, mini glass snow globe as my Christmas present. Snow globes are the world in miniature. \r\n\r\nI was so attracted to the creativity and craftsmanship of this snow globe. On the outside, there is a grey cat. Inside the  globe, there is a 24K gold computer mouse hiding. I am a cat lover, so for Raymond to choose this globe for me is very meaningful and it has become the symbol of our love. This is my favorite and the most treasurable globe in my entire collection. \r\n\r\nFrom then on, whenever and wherever I go shopping, I will look for mini size glass snow globe and collecting mini snow globe became my hobby. \r\n\r\nAt first, I was only able to buy mini globes in some gift shops in Hong Kong. I was able to acquire more when I travel. Relatives and friends started buying snow globe for me as gifts. Raymond and my parents have been the key contributors and supporters to my collection. In 2003, I discovered EBAY auction, so I start bidding and buying mini globes from the internet. Major snow globe producers promote new globes every year, famous ones include: Westland, Kurl Adler, Twinkle and Disney. \r\n',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:0;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:1;s:5:\"buddy\";b:1;s:7:\"message\";b:1;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2008-12-15 22:06:04'),(838,850,'casual','1986-04-13','m','11598','United States','US','','','','Cards/Coins',0,0,'','',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:1;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:1;s:5:\"buddy\";b:1;s:7:\"message\";b:1;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2008-12-16 09:25:47'),(839,851,'casual','1973-02-25','f','11221','United States','US','','I come from a long line of pack-rats, aka collectors! I pretty much collect anything that touches my life in some way...\r\n\r\nI\'m a native New Yorker, visual artist, jackie of all trades! ','I collect tins, matchbooks, Christmas ornaments/decorations, Celtic memorabilia, magnets, buttons, pins, dvds, cds, purses, etc....\r\n\r\nThe list just goes on & on!!','Tons of Things!!',200,1000,'5+ times a year','I collect so many things, all close to my heart and based on something important in my life...',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:1;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:1;s:5:\"buddy\";b:1;s:7:\"message\";b:1;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2008-12-16 11:22:56'),(840,852,'casual','1967-10-15','f','07014','United States','US','','I grew up in Brooklyn and Now I have been transplanted to NJ.  Oh I am also a proud Soccer, Basketball, Lacrosse MOM.','I collected these Beanies when I was younger.  Some of them were minis to match my full size ones.','beanie babies',9,50,'3 times a year','I make beaded jewelry. and I drive all over to take my kid to sports events.',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:1;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:1;s:5:\"buddy\";b:1;s:7:\"message\";b:1;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2008-12-16 11:24:09'),(841,853,'casual','1920-01-01','m','522004','United States','US','','','','',0