y joined the Flickr community I realized that I also have many vintage Pyrex and other glassware objects which I had never collected as such but acquired because they were attractive and useful in the kitchen. I have also not, until recently, separated out my objects into categories, but that is changing.\r\nI am not an expert on plastics materials but like to think I know something about aesthetics and design. I choose my objects based on their design aesthetics and this will mostly include \'good design\' but also \'bad design\' and \'mad or crazy design\'.','domestic plastics, mostly poost WWII',10,0,'','Product design, the designed environment, furniture design, travel (in my motorhome), country music, home cooked food, my family.',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:1;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:1;s:5:\"buddy\";b:1;s:7:\"message\";b:1;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2009-04-29 16:19:02'),(1173,1193,'casual','1987-11-24','m','28403','United States','US','shadowwolf09','I dont know much about myself right this moment, it doesn\'t matter anyways, Im a buyer & a collector & planning to enjoy life & make good money','I collect JP toys because I\'ve grew up with it\r\n& love JP toys when I was a boy. ','Jurassic park toys',400,400,'5+ times a month','movies, wild life photography, producing videos,\r\nalot of things',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:1;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:1;s:5:\"buddy\";b:1;s:7:\"message\";b:1;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2009-04-29 17:28:35'),(1174,1194,'serious','1949-08-09','f','18355','United States','US','','Retired from a vaccine manufacturing company a few years ago. I have two Daughters, a Grandson and a Granddaughter. Enjoy going to flea markets, yard sales and antique shows in search of additions to my collection. Belong to the Novelty Salt and Pepper Shakers Club for 20 years. Also enjoy nature and bird watching.','Received my Grandmothers salt and pepper shake