 a space history expert and, as described by MSNBC, \"a respected appraiser of the value of spaceflight memorabilia.\"\r\n\r\nPearlman is a member of the U.S. Space Walk of Fame Foundation Board of Directors, serves on the Advisory Committee of the Ansari X PRIZE Foundation and on the nominating induction committee for the Astronaut Hall of Fame in Florida. He is a director emeritus of the National Space Society and former national chair of the Students for the Exploration and Development and Space (SEDS).\r\n\r\nIn 2001, his work on collectSPACE earned Pearlman the Collector of the Year Award from the Universal Autograph Collectors Club (UACC). In 2009, Pearlman was inducted into the Space Camp Hall of Fame.','','space memorabilia',0,0,'','',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:1;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:0;s:5:\"buddy\";b:0;s:7:\"message\";b:0;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2009-07-20 09:28:11'),(1364,1384,'casual','1980-03-28','m','2000','Australia','AU','','I have been collecting M&M\'s dispensers since 1997 but being in Australia they are hard to come by but I\'ve managed to pick up some nice ones around Australia and overseas.','Mainly M&M\'s dispensers plus a few other things, like handheld games, clocks, watches, PC mouse etc but there\'s too much dodgy stuff out there which Mars Inc is pumping out so I try to only buy the \"quality\" merchandise nowadays that doesn\'t blow the budget.','M&M\'s dispensers and stuff',100,50,'2 times a year','Tennis, BBall and Taekwondo... afterall, a geek needs to protect oneself ^_^',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:0;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:1;s:5:\"buddy\";b:1;s:7:\"message\";b:1;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2009-07-20 11:37:19'),(1365,1385,'casual','1989-06-24','m','61611','United States','US','none','ive always wanted a turbo helmet','none','nothing',0,0,'1 time a year','i really like power rangers morphers and helmets',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_a