 an RIAA issued platinum record and an album signed by all the band members. I bought a new car and after really enjoying the way it handled I collected as many Dodge Magnums toy cars I could find. That also led into die-cast model cars, but that died out very quickly when I realized how many cars that were out there that I wanted. I have tamed my collecting desires quite a bit. But when I visit Disneyland I can\'t help but over do it on the pins.','an assortment of items.',250,0,'','My main interest is photography, and now I collect items that allow me to take better photos. \r\nVisit www.flickr.com/photos/conceptsbynicholaslopez.com',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:0;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:1;s:5:\"buddy\";b:1;s:7:\"message\";b:1;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2009-08-23 19:26:52'),(1463,1483,'casual','1960-11-23','m','78249','United States','US','',NULL,NULL,'',0,0,'','',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:1;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:1;s:5:\"buddy\";b:1;s:7:\"message\";b:1;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2009-08-23 23:21:32'),(1464,1484,'obsessive','1965-03-22','m','90010','United States','US','WWW.TIMETOYAGERS.COM/BKEMPER','A FISH FANATIC!','OVER THE YEARS I\'VE COLLECTED HUNDREDS, MAYBE EVEN THOUSANDS OF VINTAGE FISH, MERMAID, SEAHORSE AND WHALE PIECES.  ALL FROM THE 1950\'S.  I\'VE SOLD OFF MOST OF MY COLLECTIONS AND NOW AM SELLING THE FINAL FEW ITEMS THAT REMAIN.','VINTAGE FISH',300,5000,'','',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:1;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:1;s:5:\"buddy\";b:1;s:7:\"message\";b:1;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2009-08-24 06:12:02'),(1465,1485,'casual','1970-08-25','m','48223','United States','US','',NULL,NULL,'',0,0,'','',0,NULL,'a:3:{s:8:\"show_age\";b:1;s:6:\"msg_on\";b:1;s:11:\"invite_only\";b:0;}','a:3:{s:7:\"comment\";b:1;s:5:\"buddy\";b:1;s:7:\"message\";b:1;}','2010-02-11 10:43:59','2009-08-25 17:24:35'),(1466,1486,'casual','